name: createGeneralLedgerEntryUsingSustainabilityAccounts

testSteps.description: Given that I'm logged in to 'General Ledger Entry' page

children.description: When i open page from sidebar menu: {General Ledger,General Ledger Entries}

exception.message: Expected condition failed: waiting for visibility of element located by By.xpath: //div[@class = 'sidebar-menu-container'] (tried for 10 second(s) with 100 milliseconds interval)

testSteps.description: Then the 'G/L Header Information' page should show up
When I set the currency to 'USD'
When I set the description to 'TEST1'
When I click 'Continue' button
Then the 'G/L Distribution' page should show up
When I set the Account Number to '960001'
Then the Line Description placeholder should be set to 'PREMISE CODE/Consumption Period'
When I set the Line Description to 'TEST1'
When I set the Amount to '1000'
When I set the Cost Center to 'DAV2000'
When I set the General Obj to 'AFGHAIG'
When i click show next button
When I set the Units to '21'
Then the Unit of Measure should be set to 'Cubic Metre'
When I set the 'Line Ref' to 'AF-HER-ASSENG-07-1-0001'
When i click on add line button
When i click on the last line
When I set the Account Number to '960002'
Then the Line Description placeholder should be set to ',PREMISE CODE/Consumption Period'
When I set the Line Description to 'TEST1'
When I set the Amount to '1000'
When I set the Cost Center to 'DAV2120'
When I set the General Obj to 'AFGHAIG'
When i click show next button
When I set the Units to '10'
Then the Unit of Measure should be set to 'Kilowatt Hour'
When I set the 'Line Ref' to 'AF-HER-ASSENG-07-1-0001'
When i click on add line button
When i click on the last line
When I set the Account Number to '960003'
Then the Line Description placeholder should be set to 'PREMISE CODE/Consumption Period'
When I set the Line Description to 'TEST1'
When I set the Amount to '1000'
When I set the Cost Center to 'AMM2100'
When I set the General Obj to 'AFGHAIG'
When i click show next button
When I set the Units to '30'
Then the Unit of Measure should be set to 'Cubic Metre'
When I set the 'Line Ref' to 'AF-HER-ASSENG-07-1-0001'
When i click on add line button
When i click on the last line
When I set the Account Number to '960004'
Then the Line Description placeholder should be set to 'PREMISE CODE/Consumption Period'
When I set the Line Description to 'TEST1'
When I set the Amount to '1000'
When I set the Cost Center to 'DAM1000'
When I set the General Obj to 'AFGHAIG'
When i click show next button
When I set the Units to '40'
Then the Unit of Measure should be set to 'Giga Calories'
When I set the 'Line Ref' to 'AF-HER-ASSENG-07-1-0001'
When i click on add line button
When i click on the last line
When I set the Account Number to '948001'
Then the Line Description placeholder should be set to 'PREMISE CODE/Paper Size/Delivery Date'
When I set the Line Description to 'TEST1'
When I set the Amount to '1000'
When I set the Cost Center to 'AMM5000'
When I set the General Obj to 'AFGHAIG'
When i click show next button
When I set the Units to '1'
Then the Unit of Measure should be set to 'Ream'
When I set the 'Line Ref' to 'AF-HER-ASSENG-07-1-0001'
When I click the 'Select Cash' Button
Then the 'Select CASH Account' modal should show up
When I select first checkbox from 'Select Cash' modal
When I click 'Submit' button
When I click 'Proceed' button
Then the 'General Ledger Entry successfully created' modal should show up
